Plan:
1. Add `src/stats.rs` with public `RunStats` and `ScorerStats` types matching Section 5.9/6.1.
2. Implement `RunResult::stats()` and `RunResult::stats_with(confidence_level)` there, using the existing `RunResult`/`Score` shapes directly.
3. Aggregate per-scorer results across all samples, excluding `Err(ScorerError)` outcomes from score denominators while counting them in `RunStats.total_errors`.
