5. Compute Binary pass_rate, pass_at_k, pass_all_k, and Wilson confidence intervals from scored trials only.
6. Compute Label distributions and mode, plus a deterministic `RunStats::summary()`.
7. Add focused public API tests for numeric/metric, binary, label, single-trial behavior, and error exclusion, then run `cargo fmt` and `cargo test`.
